{"type": "article", "id": 6865, "title": "2015 索尼世界摄影奖", "description": "Best On The Web 是一个推荐性栏目，每个工作日我们会从互联网世界中找出最好看的内容，希望这个栏目让我们始终与阅读、知识和美好在一起。", "date": "2015-02-27T08:15:07Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 153, "name": "摄影"}, {"id": 7292, "name": "纪实摄影"}, {"id": 1012, "name": "自然"}, {"id": 186, "name": "索尼"}], "category": 12, "author": 13, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 25, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605210925HM4xuQPY7m5BpyK6.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<strong>The Atlantic</strong>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<strong><a href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/photo/2015/02/the-2015-sony-world-photography-awards/386072/?utm_source=nextdraft&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\">The 2015 Sony World Photography Awards</a></strong> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t 很多时候，图片依然是讲述故事的最佳方式。比如你看到<strong><a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/features/2015-02-25/junk-on-the-trunk?utm_source=nextdraft&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\">这些在意大利西西里的西勒莫那些车上能够堆放的如此庞杂的废物</a></strong>。想象一下你如何往自己的车上绑上这么多东西，这简直不可思议。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210922bNunLV1G0frIMeUy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t又或者是一位摄影师经过多年拍摄记录下来的<strong><a href=\"http://www.citylab.com/commute/2015/02/the-fantastic-transformation-of-subway-cars-into-artificial-reefs/385877/?utm_source=nextdraft&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\">城市中的地铁车厢，如何成为了大西洋中的暗礁</a></strong>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210922V8M6yw9fn7THrFLX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t刚刚诞生的<strong><a href=\"http://www.theatlantic.com/photo/2015/02/the-2015-sony-world-photography-awards/386072/?utm_source=nextdraft&amp;utm_medium=email\" target=\"_blank\">索尼世界摄影奖获奖者</a></strong>来自从 171 个国家中择选出来的超过 17 万张照片。主题覆盖自然、战事和日常生活形态。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210922PKpiRkNF0DYlLUdE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tRestricted Area\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210923LQx58hVOmEeGYkAt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tAn aerial photograph of the Adriatic coastline between Ravenna and Rimini, Italy. \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605210924sEyz3OTDBQ8cwVd7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tBlack days of Ukraine, 1. Part of a series of photos taken in June and July near the city of Luhansk, Ukraine. \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052109240QH5vMI2RZnydeTB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\tThe Reflection.\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}